OL,3,CCovid inquiry rejects bid from Mone to
OL,4,Cbe 'core participant'
OL,6,FA bid from Baroness Michelle Mone and
OL,7,Fher husband to access documents and
OL,8,Fother evidence about personal
OL,9,Fprotective equipment (PPE) deals in
OL,10,Fthe pandemic has been rejected by the
OL,11,FUK Covid-19 Inquiry.
OL,13,FThe inquiry's chairwoman, Baroness
OL,14,FHeather Hallett, rejected an
OL,15,Fapplication from Lady Mone and Doug
OL,16,FBarrowman to become so-called core
OL,17,Fparticipants as past the deadline and
OL,18,Fsaid she would have rejected it anyway
OL,19,Fas she did not accept they had a
OL,20,F"direct or significant" role in the
OL,21,Fmatters the inquiry is investigating.
