OL,3,CCovid inquiry rejects bid from Mone to
OL,4,Cbe 'core participant'
OL,6,FThe inquiry began four weeks of
OL,7,Fscrutiny of decisions to purchase PPE
OL,8,Fon Monday.
OL,10,FThe Tory peer, 52, and Mr Barrowman,
OL,11,F59, have faced controversy over the
OL,12,F"VIP lane" contracts granted to some
OL,13,Fsuppliers during the coronavirus
OL,14,Fpandemic.
OL,16,FPPE Medpro, a consortium led by Mr
OL,17,FBarrowman, was awarded government
OL,18,Fcontracts worth more than #200 million
OL,19,Fto supply personal protective
OL,20,Fequipment after Lady Mone recommended
OL,21,Fit to ministers.
