OL,6,FLady Mone and Mr Barrowman applied to
OL,7,Fbecome core participants on February
OL,8,F27, 468 days after the deadline of
OL,9,FNovember 17 2023.
OL,11,FThis would have given them a special
OL,12,Fstatus to receive documents, suggest
OL,13,Fquestions and get advance notice of
OL,14,Fthe inquiry's report.
OL,16,F"I do not accept that applicants have
OL,17,Fa direct or significant role in the
OL,18,Fmatters to be investigated by the
OL,19,Finquiry," Lady Hallett said in her
OL,20,Fdecision.
