OL,6,F"Whilst Medpro was a significant
OL,7,Fsupplier of PPE to the UK government,
OL,8,Fit was but one of a number of such
OL,9,Fsuppliers and there are several other
OL,10,Fcontracts that the inquiry is
OL,11,Finvestigating."
OL,13,FIt comes after the inquiry decided
OL,14,Fthat evidence about PPE Medpro will be
OL,15,Fheard in private to avoid prejudicing
OL,16,Fan ongoing police investigation into
OL,17,Fthe company.
