OL,6,FNaomi Fulop, from the Covid-19
OL,7,FBereaved Families for Justice UK
OL,8,Fgroup, said: "The inquiry's
OL,9,Finexplicable decision to protect these
OL,10,Fcorporations from public scrutiny
OL,11,Fsmacks of a potential whitewash and
OL,12,Fmakes achieving real justice for the
OL,13,FCovid-19 bereaved families less
OL,14,Flikely."
OL,16,FBut the Covid-19 inquiry argued that
OL,17,Fit does not need to hear evidence from
OL,18,Fcompanies about specific PPE orders.
